metadata.name: Reach
metadata.description:
When I heard the tick of clock, I am far beyond words, so far inside the world I was only an atom, a song singing to itself, a song that always accompanies me, inside my solitude. 
My wish to speak a language of high flung music and earthliness.

February 19, 2023 // Mada Kusuma
